 <title>VICAS INTRODUCTION</title>
 <link>http://boa.gov.vn/en/vicas-introduction</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-dichvu-phamvi field-type-markup field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-dichvu-noi-dung field-type-text-long field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, Tahoma, &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;VIETNAM CERTIFICATION ACCREDITATION SCHEME (VICAS)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The Vietnam Certification Accreditation Scheme (VICAS) - one of accreditation schemes of Bureau of Accreditation (BoA) is&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Organized and operated in compliance with the requirements of ISO/IEC 17011:2004;&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Member of International Accreditation Forum (IAF) and Pacific Accreditation Cooperation (PAC);&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Member of IAF Multilateral Recognition Arrangement for Quality Management System (QMS), Food safety Management System (FSMS) and Product Certification (PRODUCT).&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Accreditation schemes&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
VICAS provides accreditation service to all local and overseas certification bodies which carry out the certification of:&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Quality Management System (QMS);&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Environment Management System (EMS);&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Food Safety Management System (FSMS);&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Product certification (PRODUCT);&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Personnel certification; and&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Other Management Systems as required.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Accreditation Criteria&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
For accreditation of QMS and EMS Certification Bodies&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;ISO/IEC 17021/ ISO/IEC 17021-1: Requirements for bodies providing audit and certification of management systems;&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;ISO/IEC TS 17021-2: Competence requirements for auditing and certification of environmental management systems;&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;ISO/IEC TS 17021-3: Competence requirements for auditing and certification of quality management systems;&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;IAF Mandatory documents.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;For accreditation of Product Certification Bodies&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;ISO/IEC 17065: Conformity assessment – Requirements for bodies certifying products, processes and services.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;For accreditation of FSMS Certification Bodies&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;ISO/TS 22003: Food safety management systems – Requirements for bodies providing audit and certification of food safety management systems;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;For accreditation of Personnel Certification Bodies&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;ISO/IEC 17024: Conformity assessment - Requirements for bodies operating certification of persons.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Benefits of Accreditation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;To provide confidence for customers and concerning parties in the credibility and objectivity of certification bodies;&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;To encourage the multilateral recognition of certification among nations;&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;To strengthen the unity in the operation of the certification in Vietnam and support for the implementation of management systems.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, Tahoma, &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
